{"tid":819713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖「山竹」經過國境之南 中國遊客無懼巨浪搶拍照","createTime":"2018-09-15T04:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T04:38:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c29c55f1b378107dc0239b7a5b3c845bc9016e0c","tid":819713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpltCjo1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpltCjo1.jpg&h=4fc3a5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恐怖強颱「山竹」雖未登陸台灣，但強大威力從鵝鑾鼻南方海域經過，掀起恆春半島巨浪風雨，民眾大多進入屋內躲避，唯有「勇敢」中客無懼風雨，好奇到海邊觀浪拍照留念。<br />\n<br />\n恆春半島受到「山竹」外圍影響，一早就出現明顯風雨，超過10級陣風狂吹，南灣、小灣、船帆石等海域掀起超過4米大浪，墾管處自昨起已封閉所有海域遊憩活動。<br />\n<br />\n墾丁地區雖然僅間歇雨勢，但海邊風浪驚人，不少中國遊客對於巨浪好奇，不懼頻頻拍打上岸的風浪，無視雨傘被吹走開花，堅持留下紀念照，讓不少居民直呼「原來這就是狼性。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpAflXUW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpAflXUW.jpg&h=8f4b372e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2551884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2551884&d=XHq8fknx0xpBd2vv980h454%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=fdf0b351\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2551884&h=fa3390b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2551884</a>"},{"pid":"bd837fcd404e084557c25eb087d6b105a009d1b8","tid":819713,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T04:38:16.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩 爛命一條"}]}